<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v8" title="Q30_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Diego, Marcela y Janet juntan dinero para comprar bebidas y snacks que revenderán en un partido de fútbol. En total invierten <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos: Diego aporta <m:math><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos, Marcela <m:math><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos y Janet el resto.</p>
    <p>Después venden todo y obtienen <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos. Quieren repartir ese dinero en forma proporcional al aporte de cada uno. A continuación se muestran cuatro posibles formas de repartir esos <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos entre Diego, Marcela y Janet (en ese orden).</p>
    <p>¿Cuál de los siguientes repartos es coherente con un reparto proporcional al aporte de cada uno?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">Diego: $26 666,67; Marcela: $26 666,67; Janet: $26 666,67.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Un reparto proporcional debe respetar la razón de los aportes. Janet aporta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que los aportes quedan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En esta opción los tres reciben lo mismo, o sea <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>26&#160;666,67</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>26&#160;666,67</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>26&#160;666,67</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y esa razón no coincide con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">Diego: $32 000; Marcela: $24 000; Janet: $24 000.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Janet aporta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que la razón de aportes es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. La suma de las partes es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que de <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos a Diego le corresponden <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>de</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, a Marcela <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>de</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y a Janet <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>de</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">Diego: $36 000; Marcela: $22 000; Janet: $22 000.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Janet aporta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que la razón correcta es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En esta opción los montos quedan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>36&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>22&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>22&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Si fuera proporcional, Diego debería recibir exactamente <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>de</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, y Marcela y Janet deberían recibir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>de</m:mo><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> cada una. Esta opción no cumple esos valores.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">Diego: $29 333,33; Marcela: $25 333,33; Janet: $25 333,33.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Janet aporta <m:math><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos, así que los aportes son <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso, del total de <m:math><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos, a Diego le corresponden <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>40</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> del total, es decir <m:math><m:mn>32&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>, y a Marcela y Janet <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>%</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> cada una, es decir <m:math><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> cada una. Los montos <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>29&#160;333,33</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>25&#160;333,33</m:mn><m:mo>;</m:mo><m:mn>25&#160;333,33</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> no coinciden con ese reparto proporcional.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso: reparto proporcional según los aportes</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular el aporte de Janet</strong></p>
            <p>El total invertido es <m:math><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> pesos.</p>
            <p>Diego aporta <m:math><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> y Marcela aporta <m:math><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces, Janet aporta el resto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>40&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, los aportes son:</p>
            <p>Diego: $16 000, Marcela: $12 000, Janet: $12 000.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Escribir la razón de los aportes</strong></p>
            <p>La razón es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>16&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>12&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Dividiendo cada término por <m:math><m:mn>4000</m:mn></m:math>, queda:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Repartir los 80 000 pesos según esa razón</strong></p>
            <p>La suma de las partes es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces cada parte vale:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>80&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos.</p>
            <p>Ahora calculamos lo que recibe cada persona:</p>
            <p>Diego: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Marcela: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Janet: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>8000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>El reparto proporcional correcto es:</p>
            <p>Diego: $32 000; Marcela: $24 000; Janet: $24 000.</p>
            <p>Esto coincide exactamente con la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La opción coherente con un reparto proporcional al aporte de cada uno es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>